title.narrative: Consolidating Democracy in Pakistan – Management costs

description.narrative: This activity (Consolidating Democracy in Pakistan – Management costs) is a component of Consolidating Democracy in Pakistan (CDIP) Programme. reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,867,765. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Democratic participation and civil society, Elections. The start date is 01-01-2016 and the end date is 31-03-2021.

owner-org.narrative: UK - Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (FCDO)
